Class CreateElectionTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • CreateElectionTest
  • public class CreateElectionTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is in charge of reading a processing the ballot CSV files. It should process the ballot CSV and return the correct election type. This class will exit the program if there is a problem Identifying the ballot file or the ballot file is incorrectly formatted.
